{"tid":2505654,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港算唔算文化沙漠？點解會有文化沙漠出現？","createTime":"2021-04-26T18:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T19:01:15.000Z","uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"255412e3e9276a4db62805b2c1ee94846cf4cce0","tid":2505654,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:56:02.000Z","msg":"之前聽一個讀中文嘅朋友講話香港人普遍文化素養低，唔睇書，連讀中文嘅都唔睇書，然後我問我身邊啲老友，又係話唔睇書嘅，一睇就瞓，點解會咁嘅？<br />\n今日我大概同身邊啲朋友討論下咗，據說文化沙漠呢隻字係80年代出現？有人話係因為資本主義社會太發達，後工業時期同埋單度向社會造成咁；又有人話係教育方式出錯；又有人話係兩者結合，因為資本主義社會太過傾斜導致到教育方式出錯，大家又點睇？"},{"pid":"316dfac7cf07d631fa5347c008985c44be513ceb","tid":2505654,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T18:59:08.000Z","msg":"更正，單向度*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話因為咁造咗一浸好表面嘅流行文化出嚟，流於表面而無深度嘅，呢種文化通常係好快速嘅，無咩內涵，全部都係流於表面嗰浸，大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係學下嘢嘅"},{"pid":"fd7d36c3956664d6be2b1ea70e1b11119b81a817","tid":2505654,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T19:01:13.000Z","msg":"細既要讀書溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大左要返工搵錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇書時間攞去溫書搵錢唔好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係好似昆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr